      "review_summary": "This PR makes Copilot registration optional-chain `api.runtime.state.openSyncKeyedStore`, logs a warning when it is absent, and registers the harness without a `sessionStore`.\n\nPR surface: Source +9. Total +9 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main's CLI metadata path passes `runtime: {} as PluginRuntime` while Copilot dereferences `api.runtime.state.openSyncKeyedStore`. I did not execute the reporter-equivalent installed CLI path in this read-only review.",
